Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 后藤?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀 没事吧 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库利玛把两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没能阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上把我送到拉库利玛去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠这里的东西来制作延展系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是吵架的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀 你…记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 鸢 想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话 是可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那小鬼们带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没什么事发生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我感觉到了非常强烈的空间扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧 刚才的光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田小姐 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正准备去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田小姐有量子计算机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器还只是个模型 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比冯•诺依曼型要好的多
