Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要生活在地下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像地上不能生存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来到底发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像发生了什么不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是被什么奇怪的东西袭击了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所大家就都搬到地下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全听不懂啊 这个说明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 我们的未来竟然变成了这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说并不是只有这个未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说我们的未来不是只有一个 而是有很多个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 未来就是未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难说明 但是时空这东西随着时间的改变有无数个存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这里只是可能性之一的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性之一的未来?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱? 为什么爱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个世界的爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次还带着男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小美保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丽丽 美保是妈妈的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的是个笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 你难道不知道龙骑兵都在找你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我虽然知道 但是因为被带到这里来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 干什么说的像别人的事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~再这样下去又要被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~那又要被塞到水槽里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 去阿姨那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 为什么会到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你是佑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人怀念啊 还只有12岁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是爱吗 难道不觉得她太亲切了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 到里面来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龙骑兵发现了就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 感觉好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被听到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 到正下方来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充电电池
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把两人都带回来 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被逆算固定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实鸢也这么说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是难懂的话?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 如果不考虑下让你们回去的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由我来保护遥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和那家伙约定过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护遥啊 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的话一定要去那个房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来时的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移装置的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿来喝的东西了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使…使不出力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 振作一点 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大哥哥的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我要在这里 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥 呼吸都没有了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 有微小点侵入拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸢 鸢回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么不让我进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑…佑会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 你是一个坚强的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 你听着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在发生了量子革命的我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的物体都进入了量子状态之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空整体就是一个无法确定的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类自身也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…是没有观测者的不安定的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测者?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们把一切都灵子技术化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并存入量子计算机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此让这个世界安定化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把这个世界命名为拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 没有数据技术化的人类 是不能存在在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以佑他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不是好好的在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前来的时候就已经被记录下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 从这里开始是重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实佑看上去像死了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要那个存在是不安定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的死也是暧昧的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是说佑现在处于死的时空和生的时空重迭的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了的佑和活着的佑?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着的佑也在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所以你不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩的你拥有把看到的东西固定化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在的你看到了死的状态的佑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑的死就会成为确实的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:11:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能看到活着的状态的佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并意识到互相的存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑的活着的状态就会被确定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么活着的佑在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是天堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我已经不能读透时空的意识了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑在香格里拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想救他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就和我一起去香格里拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧 你背叛了拉库利玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被让龙之转矩逃走的你说教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你想要帮助杀了枭的鸦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 爱 不是鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇和佑到最后还是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他还说想要见爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鸦 是诺因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我讨厌香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧 我不会把遥交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救佑 我必须去香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去的话 佑就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库利玛就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底就是那点程度的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空的收缩不仅仅是香格里拉的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是整顿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要的东西的消失是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 你也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时空接受了这根线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受到了比预想还要难以忍受的痛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有一切只有痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空的存在只是为了尝受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我在香格里拉就可以被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有龙之转矩 就可以让香格里拉接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那个没有痛苦 可以幸福的生活的时空去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们所向往的幸福的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们所向往的? 那大家在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有形态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个只依靠意识而存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去 否则佑会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把佑救回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺因 让我去香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是救了我和勇的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我和你也见过一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是藤原勇15年以后的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 那个勇被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是15年后的你杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年后的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鸦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 因为我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未来注定要杀死自己的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 那是骗人的——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉 终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到永恒的香格里拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都追到这里来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话一定能成为那样的龙骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是象我这样难堪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我这幅模样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望来香格里拉的结果就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我吧 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑愚蠢的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他解体了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佑在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生活在无限的不幸之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到死为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快睁开眼
